main: ^It showcases a massive limestone formation. Callao cave also known as "The seven-chamber show cave" and the best tourist attraction of the Cagayan Province. It is situated in the foothills of Northern Sierra Madre.

c-0: ^It is famous for being a skylit chapel and known for discovering a new species of man called the Homo Luzonensis that lived between 50,000 and 67,000 years ago in 2007.
